channel.title: My Model - Sunglasses
channel.description:
i got bored and fort ide try make something on meta.. i did this before in like 2009 when i tried to make a sword i dont have the picture anymore all you need to know is that it didnt look like a sword :) this is my 2nd Model well 1st model that is 3D :)
well heres my Sunglasses they are easily recolourable in the rar download there is the dat files and the mqo files.
Heres the Pictures:
[IMG]http://i300.photobucket.com/albums/nn22/lukesh8000/front.png[/img][IMG]http://i300.photobucket.com/albums/nn22/lukesh8000/greensunglasses.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i300.photobucket.com/albums/nn22/lukesh8000/greensunglassesonmodel.png[/img][IMG]http://i300.photobucket.com/albums/nn22/lukesh8000/sideview.png[/img]
Heres the download link:
http://uppit.com/ssonwuh69ne2/sunglasses.rar
---------------------------------------------------------------
How to recolour the glasses for them who dont know..
Download Metaseq (google it to download)
open the MQO file
Then
[IMG]http://i300.photobucket.com/albums/nn22/lukesh8000/1-1.png[/img]
change the colours i have put a box around what you need to change ^^^^^^^
[IMG]http://i300.photobucket.com/albums/nn22/lukesh8000/2-1.png[/img]
